message.content: cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. The paper deals with Visual Question Answering (VQA) which involves computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a data augmentation module and fine-tuning of VQA models, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves collecting and annotating a dataset, which falls under the sub-category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
